{title: The Man in Me}
{subtitle: Bob Dylan}
{key: G}
{tempo: 71}
{comment: ♩ = 71}

{start_of_grid: Intro}
| [G] . . . | [C] . [Am] . | [D] . . . | [D] . [G] . |
